snippet: A plane carrying Jenni Rivera and four other passengers crashed early Sunday morning in the mountains of northeastern Mexico. No survivors were immediately found.
abstract: Mexican-American singer and television star Jenni Rivera, along with four other passengers and two pilots, is feared to have died in plane crash in Mexico.
lead_paragraph: A plane carrying Jenni Rivera and four other passengers crashed early Sunday morning in the mountains of northeastern Mexico. No survivors were immediately found.

headline.seo: Plane Wreckage of Mexican-American Singer Jenni Rivera Found
headline.main: Mexican-American Singing Star Is Feared to Have Died in Plane Crash Near Monterrey
